ualberta.g12.adventurecreator.tasks

Class PublishStoryTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Story,Void,Boolean>
      • ualberta.g12.adventurecreator.tasks.PublishStoryTask

  • public class PublishStoryTask
extends AsyncTask<Story,Void,Boolean>
    Task used to publish a local story to the online repo of stories. If their is a story that has the same id as this story we will overwrite the existing online story.

    This task is used by a user when they want to publish their local story to the online list of stories.
